{"tid":626760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被問「有冇」警答「收到」 官：依家警隊啲質素真係……","createTime":"2018-04-12T11:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T12:21:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cd50b8c46f2655c3547bdf677f2ae7b5e627bb","tid":626760,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"警員朱文海今就一宗非禮案出庭作供，惟他甫步入證人台即坐著宣誓，要書記中途提醒警員才懂得站立。暫委裁判官許肇强即問朱何時加入警隊，朱回應稱2013年。裁判官再問：「學堂冇教你宣誓要企喺度咩？」朱卻問非所答的稱：「收到。」<br />\n<br />\n裁判官忍不住向朱道說：「問你有冇呀，收到&hellip;&hellip;」朱道歉後，裁判官仍不滿謂:「我發覺依家警隊啲質素真係&hellip;&hellip;坐返低。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180412/58065223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58065223&d=ASUwK%2Bpx0BiGpEbkl%2FvLzr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ae66ef96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58065223&h=15e34080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180412/58065223</a>"},{"pid":"eb47e0a5285be558f61d3aef9e2ade9a6c48cf57","tid":626760,"uid":60709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"呢d狗係要撚下"},{"pid":"ae64c46fc055b441892ce8766623626fe4a0a268","tid":626760,"uid":147770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"毅進程度..... 坐返底"},{"pid":"269104a41d1df3474e5a8ac839898a16f528ae16","tid":626760,"uid":2333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"代表平時散仔心態囉<br />\n你叫我做乜  你屌我   <br />\n<br />\n都係一句收到就搞撚掂   唔洗思考  只要服從<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a07c376a67e1234270dd28df697c9ec6f01975","tid":626760,"uid":22574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:19:46.000Z","msg":"係法庭柒一次唔夠<br />\n仲要上黎柒多次<img src=\"/assets/fa